-- XL Capital to buyback $1 bln Class A shares
-- 
-- Mon Feb 26, 2007 9:10am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/02/26/businesspro-xlcapital-buyback-dc-idUSWNAS206820070226

 

 (Reuters) - Reinsurer XL Capital Ltd ( XL.N ) said its board 
authorized the repurchase of up to $1 billion of its Class A 
ordinary shares. 


  The company said the new repurchase program includes the 
unused $135.4 million allocated to a share repurchase program 
authorized in January, 2000.  (Reporting by Sayantani Ghosh in Bangalore)